**  TBL1/TBL2 (UPDATE /NAME)
0 CANCEL
1 CHANGE
2 ADD
**  TBL3/TBL4 (FACTORY /NAME)
0111IAF F
**  TBL5/TBL6 (INSTRUCTION /NAME)
ACMPL MAT
BMATERIAL
**  ER (ERROR-MESSAGE)
E-01 NOT USE LONG TIME, SIGN OFF
E-02 UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS WRONG
E-03 INPUT MANAGEMENT DEPARTMENT CODE
E-04 MANAGEMENT DEPARTMENT CODE IS WRONG
E-05 MATERIAL INSTRUCTION IS WRONG
E-06 INPUT MATERIAL
E-07 INPUT WIRE DIAMETER
E-08 THIS MATERIAL/WIRE DIAMETER ISN'T INPUT IN MATERIAL M/F
E-09 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F EXIST
E-10 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F NOT EXIST
E-11 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F WAS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-12 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F NOT EXIST
E-13 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F WAS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-14 INPUT 1 COIL WEIGHT
E-15 INPUT SUPPLIER
E-16 SUPPLIER IS WRONG
E-17 INPUT LOCATION FROM 1
E-18 INPUT NBR OF KANBAN SHEETS FROM 1
E-19 INPUT MACHINE NO FROM 1
